text: Akshat - I have a fundamental argument against Coinbase. While they have first mover advantage, they are just replicating the traditional full service broker model for crypto. They charge exorbitant fees (I know as I have an account with them) and compared to other brokers in the crypto space, its huge. Check Binance, FTX and other brokers fees v/s Coinbase. It will be only time before they lose the competitive advantage. Like what Zerodha did to full service brokers! I would caution others to look into this model and not just go by Cathy Woods recommendation  ;)
